<subSubSection id="7B3A4F602768D2FEB35262D1B00AE8C5" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" type="notes">
<paragraph id="63856602DABF8172ED5E2BEA6557B5C0" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E944814A494B3AD2220247E4BFE2C91E" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">
The basionym was published by indelible autograph on specimen labels (Arts. 30.5-6 of the ICN, 
<bibRefCitation id="EDD4D9971B60A965986B1476A66A8F5C" author="Turland, NJ" journalOrPublisher="Lagascalia" pageId="2" pageNumber="33" url="doi.org/10.12705/Code.2018" year="2018">Turland et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
, see also 
<bibRefCitation id="C6A0C82A03EE750059D83C14BB2CDCA4" author="Galasso, G" journalOrPublisher="Phytotaxa" pageId="2" pageNumber="33" pagination="77 - 86" title="Printed, or just indelible? On the earliest legitimate names, authorship and typification of the taxa described from Italy by Huter, Porta and / or Rigo." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.361.1.6" volume="361" year="2018">Galasso et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
for similar cases). Accordingly, all the duplicates of 
<taxonomicName id="5E4D2D11B4BFBB44FCB3F0D96EAF4FA8" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Rosmarinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Rosmarinus lavandulaceus" order="Lamiales" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lavandulaceus">Rosmarinus lavandulaceus</taxonomicName>
de 
<normalizedToken id="393FA3698C18C936305E2AE2597A947D" originalValue="Noé">Noe</normalizedToken>
linked to n° 444 of the exsiccata series &quot;Plantes 
<normalizedToken id="22B0CE10DE1B7D52DBE14A5325AC0E0C" originalValue="d’Algérie”">d'Algerie&quot;</normalizedToken>
, preserved in several European herbaria, are syntypes and eligible for lectotypification. The type indicated by 
<bibRefCitation id="2E96B63A035E574B80A03238DE4D9A9C" author="Rosua, JL" journalOrPublisher="Lagascalia" pageId="2" pageNumber="33" pagination="179 - 187" title="Contribucion al estudio del genero Rosmarinus L. en el Mediterraneo occidental." volume="14" year="1986">
<normalizedToken id="B5FDBC2EC9CB4659F70FAB4BE9FFC56A" originalValue="Rosúa">Rosua</normalizedToken>
(1986)
</bibRefCitation>
, although mounted on a sheet with a handwritten label different from those of series &quot;Plantes 
<normalizedToken id="D10893C6A484BF90E33FF4F5076568F0" originalValue="d’Algérie”">d'Algerie&quot;</normalizedToken>
is also original material since it represents a fragment of one of the syntypes (see also Art. 8.3, Ex. 8 of the ICN).
</paragraph>
